---
title: Smart Maple-Mustard Double Pork Chops  with Roasted Chickpea Salad
description: Sweet and savoury pork chops pair beautifully with a hearty salad of roasted chickpeas and crisp cucumbers. This definitely isn't your average pork chop dinner.

